Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.67,0:02:36.30,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}時空的旅人啊 閉上你的雙眼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.34,0:02:40.43,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}星屑を超えるスピードで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.34,0:02:40.43,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}用超越群星的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.47,0:02:44.14,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Dive into the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.47,0:02:44.14,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}潛入星海之中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.18,0:02:48.60,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}物語の始まりまで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.18,0:02:48.60,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}不斷翻滾 不停掙扎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.68,0:02:52.10,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}もがき　足掻き　続けていく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.68,0:02:52.10,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}直至故事的開始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.15,0:02:55.40,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}ゼロから抜け出す
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.15,0:02:55.40,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}擺脫零的認識
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.44,0:02:58.86,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}蒼き時代を　信じて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.44,0:02:58.86,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an2\fs45\pos(201,982.5)}と  き
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.44,0:02:58.86,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}相信蒼藍的時代
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.94,0:03:02.24,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Calling you Calling you Everywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.94,0:03:02.24,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}呼喚你 在每一個角落呼喚你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.28,0:03:05.66,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}謳え　叫べ　彷徨い人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.28,0:03:05.66,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}歌頌吧 吶喊吧 彷徨的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.74,0:03:08.91,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}遥かな願いへと
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.74,0:03:08.91,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}把所有的罪與所有的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:15.54,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}罪も　愛も　流して　go away
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:15.54,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}衝向遙遠的願望
