Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:19.13,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}震撼整個靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.17,0:03:22.38,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}命辿るHeralder
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.17,0:03:22.38,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}追求生命的使者
