Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.15,0:22:30.16,staff,NTP,0,0,203,,{\fad(0,800)}校  對\N\N{\fs33}村  漢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.15,0:22:30.16,staff,NTP,0,0,675,,{\fad(0,800)}後  期\N\N{\fs33}Ｔ　Ｒ　Ｉ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.15,0:22:30.16,staff,NTP,0,0,795,,{\fad(0,800)}ED歌詞\N\N{\fs33}vv·逸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.32,0:22:27.03,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Keep pushing on !
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.32,0:22:27.03,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}只管開拓出前進的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.28,0:22:34.12,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}We can find our promised land
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.28,0:22:34.12,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}約定之地 定然就在我們前方
